I'm coming to you here from sunny Ann Arbor, Michigan today.

00:04:06.360 --> 00:04:14.360
And I'm kind of here to talk about the Domino's data journey that we've been on, and also

00:04:14.479 --> 00:04:19.279
as I was writing some notes for my talk, I thought, well, my journey is kind of weaved

00:04:19.279 --> 00:04:20.279
in there, too.

00:04:20.279 --> 00:04:27.760
So I'd be happy to talk about my career trajectory and opportunities, roadblocks I've faced along

